snippet.title: Sonic the Hedgehog RPG: Return to Iron Lock (SAGE 2022 Trailer)
snippet.description:
Trailer for the third episode of the Sonic SatAM RPG series releasing at this year's SAGE 2022!

Music by Billy P Adams
Poster by Jonathan Dobs aka "Ink Pants"
